A vintage-style illustration of a cluttered developer's desk from a bird's eye view, featuring multiple mobile devices scattered across the surface—an old iPhone, an early Android phone, and a tablet—all connected by tangled cables to a chunky laptop computer. The desk has warm wood grain texture, coffee cup rings, and scattered sticky notes. Soft afternoon sunlight streams through a window casting long shadows. The devices' screens glow softly with abstract colorful app interfaces. The overall mood is nostalgic and industrious, capturing the hands-on experimentation of early mobile development era. Muted earth tones with pops of device screen colors. No visible text or labels on any surface.
